  "instructions": [
    "Place the foie gras in a heatproof bowl set over a pot of simmering water, ensuring the water level is below the bottom of the bowl.",
    "Steam the foie gras for 10 minutes, or until it reaches an internal temperature of 145\u00065F.",
    "Meanwhile, mix together the chopped onion, minced garlic, white wine, honey, lemon juice, and chopped thyme in a small bowl.",
    "Remove the foie gras from the heat and stir in the onion mixture until well combined."
